description:
One of the most foolish statements the left makes is that we would have a rotting produce epidemic if not for illegal immigration. And while they provide no evidence to back up that claim, their true colors shine.

Rep. Jasmine Crockett claimed that we need illegal immigrants to pick our crops because they are uneducated and an educated person would never stoop to this profession to make a living.

Crockett may or may not like to tell you she is a racist without telling you she is a racist.

Rep. Jasmine Crockett: We need illegals to pick our crops and clean our hotel rooms since the educated won't pic.twitter.com/SZwD42rL7g

title: Of course, Jasmine Crockett endorses having illegals pick her crops for her
